title: Pakistan demands joint probe to accurately establish facts on 'accidental firing' of Indian missile - Moneycontrol
content:

description: Pakistan's Foreign Office spokesperson said: "Indian decision to hold an internal court of inquiry is not sufficient since the missile ended up in Pakistani territory. Pakistan demands a joint probe to accurately establish the facts surrounding the incident."
